质来源。 </p> <div class\u003d\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-neutral-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-bolt text-primary text-2xl mb-2\"></i> <p class\u003d\"font-medium\">快速能量</p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-neutral-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-heartbeat text-primary text-2xl mb-2\"></i> <p class\u003d\"font-medium\">心脏健康</p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-neutral-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-balance-scale text-primary text-2xl mb-2\"></i> <p class\u003d\"font-medium\">丰富钾元素</p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-neutral-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-cutlery text-primary text-2xl mb-2\"></i> <p class\u003d\"font-medium\">多种吃法</p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-neutral-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-leaf text-primary text-2xl mb-2\"></i> <p class\u003d\"font-medium\">易消化</p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-neutral-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-users text-primary text-2xl mb-2\"></i> <p class\u003d\"font-medium\">适合各年龄</p> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\"> <el-tag type\u003d\"success\" size\u003d\"large\">天然能量</el-tag> <el-tag type\u003d\"success\" size\u003d\"large\">富含纤维</el-tag> <el-tag type\u003d\"success\" size\u003d\"large\">维生素B6</el-tag> <el-tag type\u003d\"success\" size\u003d\"large\">镁元素</el-tag> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <!-- 中部内容区（选项卡） --> <section id\u003d\"intro\" class\u003d\"py-12 md:py-20 bg-neutral-50\"> <div class\u003d\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"> <el-tabs v-model\u003d\"activeTab\" class\u003d\"w-full\"> <el-tab-pane label\u003d\"香蕉简介\" name\u003d\"intro-tab\"> <div class\u003d\"mt-6\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4\">香蕉的起源与历史</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed\"> 香蕉起源于东南亚地区，已有超过7000年的种植历史。最早的香蕉种植记录可追溯到公元前5000年左右的巴布亚新几内亚。随着贸易和迁徙，香蕉逐渐传播到印度、非洲和美洲等地。 </p> <h3 class\u003d\"text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4\">主要品种</h3> <div class\u003d\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-custom\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary\">卡文迪什香蕉</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600\"> 最常见的香蕉品种，占全球香蕉贸易量的90%以上。果皮呈亮黄色，果肉香甜柔软，适合直接食用。 </p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-custom\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary\">红香蕉</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600\"> 果皮呈紫红色，果肉较黄香蕉更甜，带有轻微的草莓风味。富含β-胡萝卜素和维生素C。 </p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-custom\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary\">芭蕉</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600\"> 体型较大，果皮较厚，果肉淀粉含量高，通常需要烹饪后食用。在许多热带地区是主食之一。 </p> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-custom\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary\">迷你香蕉</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600\"> 体型小巧，长度通常只有10-15厘米，口感特别甜，适合儿童和作为便携零食。 </p> </div> </div> <h3 class\u003d\"text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4\">生长环境</h3> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed\"> 香蕉是热带水果，需要温暖湿润的气候，适宜生长温度为24-32°C。它们生长在高大的草本植物上，而非树木。一棵香蕉植株通常一次只结一串香蕉，收获后植株会被砍倒，新的植株会从根部重新生长。 </p> </div> </el-tab-pane> <el-tab-pane label\u003d\"营养价值\" name\u003d\"nutrition-tab\" id\u003d\"nutrition\"> <div class\u003d\"mt-6\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6\">香蕉的营养成分</h3> <div class\u003d\"overflow-x-auto mb-8\"> <table class\u003d\"w-full bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm\"> <thead> <tr class\u003d\"bg-neutral-100 text-left\"> <th class\u003d\"px-6 py-3 text-neutral-700 font-semibold\">营养素</th> <th class\u003d\"px-6 py-3 text-neutral-700 font-semibold\">含量(100g)</th> <th class\u003d\"px-6 py-3 text-neutral-700 font-semibold\">日需求量占比</th> </tr> </thead> <tbody class\u003d\"divide-y divide-neutral-100\"> <tr class\u003d\"hover:bg-neutral-50\"> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4 font-medium\">热量</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">89 kcal</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">4.5%</td> </tr> <tr class\u003d\"hover:bg-neutral-50\"> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4 font-medium\">碳水化合物</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">22.8g</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">7.6%</td> </tr> <tr class\u003d\"hover:bg-neutral-50\"> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4 font-medium\">膳食纤维</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">2.6g</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">10.4%</td> </tr> <tr class\u003d\"hover:bg-neutral-50\"> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4 font-medium\">蛋白质</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">1.1g</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">2.2%</td> </tr> <tr class\u003d\"hover:bg-neutral-50\"> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4 font-medium\">脂肪</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">0.3g</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">0.5%</td> </tr> <tr class\u003d\"hover:bg-neutral-50\"> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4 font-medium\">钾</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">358mg</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">7.6%</td> </tr> <tr class\u003d\"hover:bg-neutral-50\"> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4 font-medium\">维生素B6</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">0.4mg</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">23.5%</td> </tr> <tr class\u003d\"hover:bg-neutral-50\"> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4 font-medium\">维生素C</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">8.7mg</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">9.7%</td> </tr> <tr class\u003d\"hover:bg-neutral-50\"> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4 font-medium\">镁</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">27mg</td> <td class\u003d\"px-6 py-4\">6.4%</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-primary/5 p-6 rounded-xl border border-primary/20\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-neutral-900\">营养亮点</h4> <ul class\u003d\"space-y-3 text-neutral-600\"> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check-circle text-primary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>香蕉是钾的极佳来源，有助于维持正常的心跳和血压。</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check-circle text-primary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>含有丰富的维生素B6，参与人体超过100种酶反应，对大脑发育和功能至关重要。</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check-circle text-primary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>含有果胶等可溶性纤维，有助于调节血糖和胆固醇水平。</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-check-circle text-primary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>天然含有色氨酸，有助于促进血清素的产生，改善情绪。</span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </el-tab-pane> <el-tab-pane label\u003d\"食用方法\" name\u003d\"recipes-tab\" id\u003d\"recipes\"> <div class\u003d\"mt-6\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6\">香蕉的多样吃法</h3> <div class\u003d\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-custom\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/292/600/400\" alt\u003d\"香蕉奶昔\" class\u003d\"w-full h-48 object-cover\"> <div class\u003d\"p-6\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-neutral-900\">香蕉奶昔</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600 mb-4\">将香蕉与牛奶、冰块一起放入搅拌机，制成美味健康的奶昔。</p> <el-button type\u003d\"primary\" size\u003d\"small\" class\u003d\"bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90\">查看食谱</el-button> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-custom\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/431/600/400\" alt\u003d\"香蕉燕麦粥\" class\u003d\"w-full h-48 object-cover\"> <div class\u003d\"p-6\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-neutral-900\">香蕉燕麦粥</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600 mb-4\">将香蕉切片加入燕麦粥中，营养丰富的早餐选择。</p> <el-button type\u003d\"primary\" size\u003d\"small\" class\u003d\"bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90\">查看食谱</el-button> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-custom\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/291/600/400\" alt\u003d\"烤香蕉\" class\u003d\"w-full h-48 object-cover\"> <div class\u003d\"p-6\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-neutral-900\">烤香蕉</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600 mb-4\">香蕉去皮后烤制，撒上肉桂粉，简单美味的甜点。</p> <el-button type\u003d\"primary\" size\u003d\"small\" class\u003d\"bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90\">查看食谱</el-button> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-custom\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/493/600/400\" alt\u003d\"香蕉松饼\" class\u003d\"w-full h-48 object-cover\"> <div class\u003d\"p-6\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-neutral-900\">香蕉松饼</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600 mb-4\">用熟透的香蕉制作的松饼，口感湿润，风味浓郁。</p> <el-button type\u003d\"primary\" size\u003d\"small\" class\u003d\"bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90\">查看食谱</el-button> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-custom\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/132/600/400\" alt\u003d\"香蕉花生酱三明治\" class\u003d\"w-full h-48 object-cover\"> <div class\u003d\"p-6\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-neutral-900\">香蕉花生酱三明治</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600 mb-4\">经典组合，提供持久能量，是理想的午餐或零食。</p> <el-button type\u003d\"primary\" size\u003d\"small\" class\u003d\"bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90\">查看食谱</el-button> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-custom\"> <img src\u003d\"https://picsum.photos/id/225/600/400\" alt\u003d\"香蕉冰淇淋\" class\u003d\"w-full h-48 object-cover\"> <div class\u003d\"p-6\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-neutral-900\">香蕉冰淇淋</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600 mb-4\">冷冻香蕉放入搅拌机搅拌，制作健康无添加的冰淇淋。</p> <el-button type\u003d\"primary\" size\u003d\"small\" class\u003d\"bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90\">查看食谱</el-button> </div> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-neutral-900\">香蕉选择与储存小贴士</h4> <ul class\u003d\"space-y-3 text-neutral-600\"> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-lightbulb-o text-primary mt-1 mr-3 text-lg\"></i> <span>选择香蕉时，根据食用时间挑选：青香蕉适合几天后食用，黄香蕉适合立即食用，带斑点的香蕉适合制作烘焙食品。</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-lightbulb-o text-primary mt-1 mr-3 text-lg\"></i> <span>香蕉储存在室温下即可，放入冰箱会使果皮变黑，但果肉不受影响。</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-lightbulb-o text-primary mt-1 mr-3 text-lg\"></i> <span>将香蕉的茎用保鲜膜包裹，可以减缓香蕉成熟的速度。</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-lightbulb-o text-primary mt-1 mr-3 text-lg\"></i> <span>熟透的香蕉可以切片冷冻，用于制作冰沙或冰淇淋。</span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </el-tab-pane> <el-tab-pane label\u003d\"健康益处\" name\u003d\"benefits-tab\" id\u003d\"benefits\"> <div class\u003d\"mt-6\"> <h3 class\u003d\"text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6\">香蕉对健康的益处</h3> <div class\u003d\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8\"> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm flex\"> <div class\u003d\"mr-4 text-primary\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-heartbeat text-3xl\"></i> </div> <div> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-neutral-900\">促进心脏健康</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600\">香蕉中的钾有助于调节血压，减少心血管疾病风险。研究表明，每天食用香蕉可以降低中风风险。</p> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm flex\"> <div class\u003d\"mr-4 text-primary\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-bolt text-3xl\"></i> </div> <div> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-neutral-900\">提升能量水平</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600\">香蕉中的天然糖分（葡萄糖、果糖和蔗糖）与纤维结合，提供持续的能量释放，是运动员的理想选择。</p> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm flex\"> <div class\u003d\"mr-4 text-primary\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-dumbbell text-3xl\"></i> </div> <div> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-neutral-900\">运动后恢复</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600\">运动后食用香蕉可以补充流失的电解质，特别是钾，有助于肌肉恢复和减少痉挛。</p> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm flex\"> <div class\u003d\"mr-4 text-primary\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-brain text-3xl\"></i> </div> <div> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-neutral-900\">改善情绪与认知</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600\">香蕉含有色氨酸，有助于产生血清素（\"快乐激素\"），可以改善情绪和减轻压力。</p> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm flex\"> <div class\u003d\"mr-4 text-primary\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-balance-scale text-3xl\"></i> </div> <div> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-neutral-900\">消化系统健康</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600\">香蕉中的纤维有助于维持肠道规律，未成熟的香蕉还含有抗性淀粉，可促进肠道健康菌群。</p> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm flex\"> <div class\u003d\"mr-4 text-primary\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-bed text-3xl\"></i> </div> <div> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-neutral-900\">改善睡眠质量</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600\">香蕉含有镁和钾，这两种矿物质有助于放松肌肉和神经系统，促进更好的睡眠。</p> </div> </div> </div> <div class\u003d\"bg-primary/5 p-6 rounded-xl border border-primary/20\"> <h4 class\u003d\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-neutral-900\">注意事项</h4> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600 mb-4\"> 虽然香蕉对大多数人来说是健康的选择，但也有一些注意事项： </p> <ul class\u003d\"space-y-2 text-neutral-600\"> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-exclamation-circle text-primary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>香蕉含有较高的天然糖分，糖尿病患者应适量食用。</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-exclamation-circle text-primary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>对乳胶过敏的人可能也会对香蕉过敏，因为它们含有相似的蛋白质。</span> </li> <li class\u003d\"flex items-start\"> <i class\u003d\"fa fa-exclamation-circle text-primary mt-1 mr-2\"></i> <span>肾脏疾病患者需要控制钾的摄入量，应咨询医生后再食用香蕉。</span> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </el-tab-pane> </el-tabs> </div> </section> <!-- 统计数据 --> <section class\u003d\"py-12 md:py-16 bg-primary/10\"> <div class\u003d\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"> <div class\u003d\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center\"> <div> <div class\u003d\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-2\" id\u003d\"counter-1\">0</div> <p class\u003d\"text-neutral-600\">全球年产量(百万吨)</p> </div> <div> <div class\u003d\"text-4xl 